<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA624_05_IH_0001</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="./../../common_practice/js/ema624_02_ih_0005.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema624_05.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema624_05_ih_0001 paging">
      <section class="title type2 score">
        <h2 data-head="1_deep_green" lang="y">비례식의 성질을 알아보려고 합니다. 비례식을 보고 물음에 답해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">외항의 곱과 내항의 곱을 각각 구해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box justify_center dir_col">
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA624_05_IH/0001_bg.png" alt="" />
              <p>2 : 5=6 : 15</p>
            </div>
            <div class="input_row">
              <span class="label_gray" lang="y">외항의 곱</span>
              2×
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="15"></math-field>
              </div>
              =
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="30"></math-field>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="input_row">
              <span class="label_gray" lang="y">내항의 곱</span>
              5×
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="6"></math-field>
              </div>
              =
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="30"></math-field>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- 해설 -->
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p>
                    (외항의 곱) = 2 × 15 = 30
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    (내항의 곱) = 5 × 6 = 30
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    비례식에서 외항의 곱과 내항의 곱은 같습니다.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="btn_area">
            <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
            <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
            <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">알맞은 말에 ○표 하세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box justify_center">
            <div class="text_area">
              <p>비례식에서 외항의 곱과 내항의 곱은 (같습니다<span>,</span>다릅니다).</p>
              <div class="boolean_wrap">
                <div>
                  <button data-answer-single="true" class="button1"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false" class="button2"></button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 해설 -->
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p>비례식에서 외항의 곱과 내항의 곱은 같습니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="btn_area">
            <!-- <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button> -->
            <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
            <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          </div>
        </article>
      </section>
    </div>
    <script>
      runAfterAppReady(() => {
        $('.page_2 .btnSubmit').click(function () {
          $('.page_2 .solve_area').addClass('active');
        });
        $('.page_2 .btnReset').click(function () {
          $('.page_2 .solve_area').removeClass('active');
        });
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
